\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
This class provides an empty implementation of \mbox{\hyperlink{interfaceit_1_1unical_1_1mat_1_1parsers_1_1asp_1_1dlv2_1_1DLV2ParserVisitor}{DLV2\+Parser\+Visitor}}, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.


\begin{DoxyParams}{Parameters}
{\em $<$\+T$>$} & The return type of the visit operation. Use \mbox{\hyperlink{}{Void}} for operations with no return type. \\
\hline
\end{DoxyParams}
